parameters.VIDEO_CODEC_PROFILE_BASELINE: 66: Baseline video codec profile. Generally used for video calls on mobile phones.

parameters.VIDEO_CODEC_PROFILE_MAIN: 77: Main video codec profile. Generally used in mainstream electronics such as MP4 players, portable video players, PSP, and iPads.

parameters.VIDEO_CODEC_PROFILE_HIGH: 100: (Default) High video codec profile. Generally used in high-resolution live streaming or television.
